snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online - Scions of Ithelia Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Prove your strength to Malacath and defend a demiplane of Oblivion in the Scions of Ithelia dungeon DLC. Venture into two perilous PvE dungeons, Oathsworn Pit and Bedlam Veil, and discover all-new stories, challenges, and rewards.

The Scions of Ithelia dungeon DLC arrives March 11 on PC/Mac and March 26 for Xbox and PlayStation consoles. 

Official Site: https://www.elderscrollsonline.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline
Instagram: https://instagram.com/elderscrollsonline

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence. Online interactions not rated by the ESRB.
